{"id": 1970, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些自己的事现在都变得不由自主了？", "description": "是我对“自己的事”理解有误，还是有人把管束当礼物？", "record_count": 1868, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171023143737VpI2TJBUzQ13lxSb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-31T03:00:04Z", "options": [{"id": 245504, "content": "挣钱和时间管理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124606}, {"id": 245505, "content": "凡是我想说“关你P事”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814778}, {"id": 245506, "content": "朋友圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638175}, {"id": 245507, "content": "一些大量耗费精力和业余时间的强制性集体活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 245509, "content": "成为了自己都不认识的人了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172499}, {"id": 245511, "content": "想找个归宿，也有了想法，却一直不放心，不敢真正去相信，每次一准备肯定想法，却又冷静的撕开旧伤疤，逼迫自己去回忆，苦了别人伤了自己，阿凯，对不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172499}, {"id": 245512, "content": "言论不自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172518}, {"id": 245514, "content": "工作 恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144220}, {"id": 245515, "content": "没赚钱的时候，敢花，赚钱了之后，买什么都小心翼翼。\n\n工作更不敢换", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659741}, {"id": 245516, "content": "不理性消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142038}, {"id": 246284, "content": "懒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174851}, {"id": 245517, "content": "结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166719}, {"id": 245518, "content": "微信头像敢换搞笑图片么？顺便把名字改成网名", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833420}, {"id": 245520, "content": "讀書", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171010}, {"id": 246288, "content": "参加了部门....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174856}, {"id": 245521, "content": "不由自主快双十一时刷淘宝，然后买了一堆东西……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171302}, {"id": 245522, "content": "要去迎合大众，否则你就是孤僻的那一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1122302}, {"id": 245523, "content": "微信，这不是比较私密的聊天嘛，为什么成为大半夜找人工作的工具。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062646}, {"id": 245525, "content": "没有人觉得最无聊的是钉钉么？来，钉一下……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172650}, {"id": 250645, "content": "找工作的时候并不能依照自己的爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191662}, {"id": 245526, "content": "微信工作群+1", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172651}, {"id": 245782, "content": "所谓原则，只不过是束缚自己天性的枷锁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173763}, {"id": 245528, "content": "生孩子。\n逼你生完，说这是你孩子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093036}, {"id": 245529, "content": "没有对我青春时期第一个喜欢的女孩表白！只能当朋友，或许连朋友都当不了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172666}, {"id": 245530, "content": "去爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 245531, "content": "纠结，导致的一些没效率、没兴趣的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080730}, {"id": 245532, "content": "生活的压力越来越力不从心，最后甚至忘记了青春时的梦想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882140}, {"id": 245533, "content": "交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000862}, {"id": 246045, "content": "失去了选择自己工作地点的权利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 